    EnsureGenerator()

    The get method of System.Windows.Controls.Panel.InternalChildren actually creates and connects the System.Windows.Controls.ItemContainerGenerator. Invoking this method ensures that this will happen. Otherwise the generator would be null until internals access the System.Windows.Controls.Panel.InternalChildren property. Info was deducted from source code review.
